{"id": "1510081860028334092", "channel_id": "1475263387553501427", "type": 0, "author_id": "1280181546527096993", "author_name": "fjantsa", "author_bot": false, "content": "## Website Update ~\nUpdated things again, today!\n\n### Database content \n  - Updates from game patch 2.5.1.3\n    - Translations updates, some character buffs, etc.\n  - Minor corrections for Saya & her wheels based on patch 2.5.1.3 data (Scalings were fine, but some descriptions were off)\n    - More things for Saya (lore entries? will be included at a later date)\n\n### D-Zone Updates\n  - Bosses now correctly map MaxHP changes when they have rouse effects \n    - e.g. Thais boss now correctly displays \"HP bars: 360.2K › 1.1M\" and has her real total HP listed, instead of the previous \"360k x2\".. My bad!\n\n### Builder V2\n  - More work on Builder V2, \n    - Sort of in a working state now, but I haven't wired the Opt-In beta yet, I'll leave a link below for anyone who wants to try it out in the meantime. Feedback welcome! \n    - Will polish more over the weekend~\n\nCurrently we have functioning Desktop/Tablet/Mobile views, hopefully most if not all features of V1 is ported over, but there's a lot of cleaning up and tiny bits and bobs to nudge around.\n\nHopefully everyone is also excited for the part 1 of the collaboration landing in... 20 minutes! 🥹\n\nhttps://skeydb.com/#/builder-v2\n-# For anyone looking to test the updated builder!\n-# There really isn't much new in terms of features, it just actually genuinely kinda works well for smaller devices and looks a bit neater!\n-# Any feedback is very welcome!", "timestamp": "2026-05-30T00:46:11.395000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1475263387553501427", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Complete Team Builder and Unit Database Resource", "forum_channel_id": "1304022827824844842", "thread_tags": ["1448212178447368322", "1448214877096251547", "1304022948000043028"]}
